<div class="full-page">
  <div class="page-content">

    <div class="page-section-float-left">
      <ul class="sub-nav">
        <li class="sub-nav-active">
          <a href="/about" class="sub-nav-active">About</a>
        </li>
        <li class="sub-nav-inactive">
          <a href="/story" class="sub-nav-inactive">Story</a>
        </li>       
        <li class="sub-nav-inactive">
            <a href="/team" class="sub-nav-inactive">Team</a>
        </li>   
        <li class="sub-nav-inactive">
            <a href="/campaign" class="sub-nav-inactive">Peer Teaching Fund</a>
        </li>
        <li class="sub-nav-inactive">
            <a href="/business" class="sub-nav-inactive">For businesses</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <center>
      <div class="marcomm-header">
        <div class="heading25 dark_grey">We believe everyone can teach andshould teach</div>
        <%= image_tag "v2/greyheader_full.png", :class => "greyheader full" %>
      </div>
    </center>
    
    <div class="page-section-float-left">
      <div class="about-hourschool-box">
        <div class="grid_5">
        <div class="heading15 marcomm">What is HourSchool?</div>
          <p>HourSchool is a social school built from your community. </p>
          <p>We believe everybody has something they can teach. People learn the most, and are most willing to learn, when they are learning from their peers.</p>
          <p>Our mission is to empower more people to become teachers, and to enjoy the emotional and financial rewards that teaching provides.</p>
          <br>
          <%= image_tag 'v2/arrow_orange_pointright.png' %>
          <a href="/story" style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; color: #ff7733">Read our founding story</a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid_6">
          <iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/24695810?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=ff9933" width="545" height="309" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <%= image_tag "v2-campaign/divider-long.png" %>
  
    <div class="clearfix" style="margin-top: 30px; padding-left: 20px">
      <div>
        <div class="heading15 marcomm">Learning should be relevant, engaging, and social.</div>
        <p class="about">Take an active role in your continued education; get a taste of something new in small, bite-sized classes; and meet some new people in your city.</p>
        <div>
          <%= image_tag "v2-about/Slide05.jpg", :style => "width: 427px; float: left" %>
        </div>
        <div>
          <%= image_tag "v2-about/Slide06.jpg", :style => "width: 427px" %>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 5px">
          <%= image_tag 'v2/arrow_orange_pointright.png' %>
          Check out all the classes <a href="/learn" style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; color: #ff7733">you can take</a> in your city.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <%= image_tag "v2-campaign/divider-long.png", :style => "margin-top: 30px" %>
  
    <div class="clearfix" style="margin-top: 30px; padding-left: 20px">
      <div>
        <div class="heading15 marcomm">Teaching is about learning, sharing, and building communities.</div>
        <p class="about">Get others excited about what you love; engage in the community, and learn from those you're teaching. Strengthen your role in your community and help unlock the knowledge your community already has.</p>
        <div>
          <%= image_tag "v2-about/Slide02.jpg", :style => "width: 427px; float: left" %>
        </div>
        <div>
          <%= image_tag "v2-about/Slide04.jpg", :style => "width: 427px" %>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 5px">
          <%= image_tag 'v2/arrow_orange_pointright.png' %>
          Learn more about <a href="/teach" style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; color: #ff7733">what you can teach</a> at HourSchool.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
       
  </div>
</div>

